9. The amphibio data includes information on ecology. Each species is classified as fossorial, terrestrial, aquatic, or arboreal. How many species are in each of these categories? Make a bar plot to visualize these results. Which category is most/ least represented in the data? Ter is the most represented and Fos is theleast reperesented.

amphibio_NA %>% 
  pivot_longer(Fos:Arb,
               names_to = "ecology_class",
               values_to = "count") %>% 
  group_by(ecology_class) %>% 
  summarise(species_numbers = sum(count, na.rm = T)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = ecology_class, y = species_numbers))+
  geom_bar(stat = "identity")

  geom_smooth(method = lm)
